<div class="comment" id="comment-47770931">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/CM30">CM30</a> 18 hours ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">Because a lot of them are built for the sole purpose of using AI for something, no matter whether that thing needs AI to begin with or (in many cases) needs to exist at all.<p>It&#x27;s the issue most trending tech has, where the majority of people trying to make use of it are grifters desperate for a quick buck rather than those who have problems that actually need solving.</div>
  
